title: Are You Already Dead?
itunes:title: Are You Already Dead?
description:
Episode 515 - Are you stuck in routines? How long are you going to allow yourself to stay there? If you don't grow out of them now, you will be stuck in your current life forever. If you want a better life, you must break free from comfort zones and that is what we will chat about today!
